@host = http://localhost:5280
@base = {{host}}/api/v1

### Users — đăng ký (201 Created)
POST {{base}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@stockradar.local",
  "password": "Demo123!",
  "displayName": "Demo User"
}

### Auth — đăng nhập / lấy token
# @name login
POST {{base}}/auth/tokens
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@stockradar.local",
  "password": "Demo123!"
}

### Market — tổng quan
GET {{base}}/market

### Sectors — top ngành
GET {{base}}/sectors?page=1&pageSize=5

### Opportunities — top cơ hội
GET {{base}}/opportunities?page=1&pageSize=5

### Signals — tín hiệu mới
GET {{base}}/signals?page=1&pageSize=10

### Radar items — scanner
GET {{base}}/radar-items?page=1&pageSize=20&breakout=true&accumulation=true

### Stocks — chi tiết mã
GET {{base}}/stocks/FPT

### Alerts — phân trang
GET {{base}}/alerts?category=All&page=1&pageSize=20

### Watchlist items — danh sách
GET {{base}}/watchlist-items
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Watchlist items — thêm (PUT idempotent)
PUT {{base}}/watchlist-items/FPT
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Watchlist items — thêm (POST body)
POST {{base}}/watchlist-items
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "HPG"
}

### Watchlist items — xóa
DELETE {{base}}/watchlist-items/FPT
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
